00:50:45.930 --> 00:50:50.510 align:middle line:84%
He is given assistance
from the Templar knights

00:50:50.510 --> 00:50:53.290 align:middle line:84%
who had pledged allegiance
even to his father who

00:50:53.290 --> 00:50:55.270 align:middle line:90%
had died many years before.

00:50:55.270 --> 00:50:56.310 align:middle line:90%
And this is all written.

00:50:56.310 --> 00:51:00.850 align:middle line:84%
