his son when the count dies.

00:51:18.910 --> 00:51:21.020 align:middle line:84%
So young Alfonso
has been groomed

00:51:21.020 --> 00:51:25.180 align:middle line:84%
by the grand master of
the Knights Hospitaller.

00:51:25.180 --> 00:51:27.500 align:middle line:84%
And then, as legend
goes, he basically

00:51:27.500 --> 00:51:30.330 align:middle line:84%
is crowned a knight on his 16th
birthday, which back then it

00:51:30.330 --> 00:51:31.529 align:middle line:90%
was the coming of age.

00:51:31.529 --> 00:51:33.820 align:middle line:84%
And many people have suspected
that the wording that he

00:51:33.820 --> 00:51:37.660 align:middle line:84%
