been indoctrinated as a Templar

00:51:37.660 --> 00:51:38.770 align:middle line:90%
knight, as well.

00:51:38.770 --> 00:51:42.720 align:middle line:84%
Well, when he finally gets
the independence of Portugal

00:51:42.720 --> 00:51:46.030 align:middle line:84%
as a nation before it becomes
a nation state later on,

00:51:46.030 --> 00:51:48.630 align:middle line:84%
first of all, he got
the independence going.

00:51:48.630 --> 00:51:49.960 align:middle line:90%
He writes a charter.

00:51:49.960 --> 00:51:53.066 align:middle line:84%
And on that charter,
unequivocally, he states--

00:51:53.066 --> 00:51:54.690 align:middle line:84%
and he's addressing
the Knights Templar

00:51:54.690 --> 00:51:58.360 align:middle line:84%
on the charter-- "In all your
works and all your deeds,

00:51:58.360 --> 00:52:01.824 align:middle line:84%
I do this because I
am also a brother."

00:52:01.824 --> 00:52:03.740 align:middle line:84%
And of course, the
Templars address themselves

00:52:03.740 --> 00:52:05.210 align:middle line:90%
to each other as brother.

00:52:05.210 --> 00:52:06.900 align:middle line:90%
Even Hugues de Payens did that.

00:52:06.900 --> 00:52:09.670 align:middle line:84%
And just to make sure that
the connection was not lost,

00:52:09.670 --> 00:52:13.830 align:middle line:84%
there's a huge Templar logo also
on that symbol of independence.

00:52:13.830 --> 00:52:16.680 align:middle line:84%
So he was a Templar
knight also all along.

00:52:16.680 --> 00:52:19.340 align:middle line:84%
So we can see quite clearly now
that the Templars, the order

00:52:19.340 --> 00:52:21.994 align:middle line:84%
of Sion and the Cistercians
basically worked together

00:52:21.994 --> 00:52:23.160 align:middle line:90%
with all of these alliances.

00:52:23.160 --> 00:52:23.940 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: With royalty.

00:52:23.940 --> 00:52:24.870 align:middle line:90%
I mean, they were the royalty

00:52:24.870 --> 00:52:27.380 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: Yeah, to create this
kingdom of heaven on Earth.

00:52:27.380 --> 00:52:29.420 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So
Portugal-- at what time

00:52:29.420 --> 00:52:32.766 align:middle line:84%
did it finally gain its
nation state status?

00:52:32.766 --> 00:52:33.890 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: It took some time.

00:52:33.890 --> 00:52:36.900 align:middle line:84%
From 1129 when it
gained its independence,

00:52:36.900 --> 00:52:39.630 align:middle line:84%
finally they had to clear
out all the Arabs out

00:52:39.630 --> 00:52:41.190 align:middle line:90%
of their territory.

00:52:41.190 --> 00:52:44.907 align:middle line:84%
And the nation state is defined
by a whole nation of people

00:52:44.907 --> 00:52:46.990 align:middle line:84%
