happened, of course,

00:52:52.241 --> 00:52:53.740 align:middle line:84%
on the feast day
of Mary Magdalene--

00:52:53.740 --> 00:52:54.580 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Of course.

00:52:54.580 --> 00:52:55.959 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: --in 1139.

00:52:55.959 --> 00:52:57.750 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And now this
is a part of history

00:52:57.750 --> 00:53:01.120 align:middle line:84%
that's, really, you're helping
rewrite because this has not

00:53:01.120 --> 00:53:02.890 align:middle line:84%
